
Actor Provide high level of writing concurrent and distribute systems
to create a actor
akka.actor.Actor will give the actor trait
akka.actor.Props
akka.event.Logging for logging

when ever you are extending the actor trait
you need to define the receive method
which will tell actor what to do when you receive some method

creating an system
val system = ActorSystem("<actor Name>")
creating and actor
val MyActor = system.actorOf(Props[MyActor], name="actorName")

